$interpreted: Yonghyeon: Juan-Yun...?
Juan-Yun: Forgive me, if you have it within you. I wish Juan-Yun could remain the way you see him in your hearts.
Juan-Yun: But now I'll do all I can... to put an end to your suffering.
Sione: Wah... Watch out! He's really out to kill us!
Yonghyeon: Why... Juan-Yun... Did you really... plan to murder us... all along?
Juan-Yun: ...I tried to stop you from knowing too much. But... it didn't turn out the way I'd hoped.
Yonghyeon: So... I understand now... I'm sorry, Soohyeon... I was wrong...
Yonghyeon: You know how to save her, don't you! Tell me!
Tica: Yonghyeon!
Yonghyeon: Get out of here, human! This is between me and him!
Sione: Run! Don't you understand what he means to do?
Tica: B-but he's gonna die!
Yonghyeon: Urghhh... Get out! Gahh!!!
Tica: Let me go!! I wanna help him!!
Sione: All we can do for him now is make sure his sacrifice isn't all for nothing!
Sione: Go go go!!
Juan-Yun: ...Nobody can escape the web that fate weaves for us...
Sione: Gwaagh...
Tica: Miss Sione!!
Tica: Your stomach's bleeding! Ah, it must be from when you were fighting for us earlier...
Sione: ...I wasn't ready...
Tica: Don't move! I'm gonna heal you!
Tica: Stop... Stop bleeding!
Sione: Enough already... I know my body. He'll catch up to us any moment now, hide yourself somewhere...
Tica: Tica never lets her teammates down! If we die, we die together—
Sione: Stop!
Sione: Don't you realize we've seen too much already? At least one of us has to get out of this alive!
Tica: But... But... Tica...
Tica: Tica... can't... I... *sob*...
Sione: You're not a kid anymore... You said that fate chose you. You have an important mission.
Sione: I can't go any further, but you have to escape. You know that.
Tica: Wah... *sob*...
Sione: ...The decisions you've no choice but to make... become your fate in the end...
Sione: Go now. Whatever happens, don't come out.
Tica: ...I'm sorry, I'm really sorry...
Juan-Yun: ...So? Miss Tica's hidden herself away... What for? You're only prolonging each others' suffering...
Sione: Gyah...
Juan-Yun: If only she'd been willing to stand up for you.
Sione: Gah... ahh...
Juan-Yun: ...Won't you come out, Miss Tica? I'm going to find you anyhow. Let's just get it over with.
Sione: HYAAAAAGH!
Tica: (...Guh... I can't... let him hear... me cry... *sob*...)
Juan-Yun: Miss Tica, Miss Sione here's nearly bled herself dry...
Sione: Tica... Don't fall for it...
Sione: Gyahh! Aghh!
Tica: (...I can't... I... c-c-can't...)
Sione: ...S... stop...
Juan-Yun: ...If you want me to stop, will you finally tell me where Miss Tica is hiding?
Sione: *cough**splutter*... Did you... murder Himawari... too...
Juan-Yun: ...I'll never forget how good she was to me.
Sione: ...Of course... you were a Dracontine... all along...
Juan-Yun: Miss Sione... Are you crying? For Himawari? Or for yourself?
Sione: No, I know I've... been so lucky. I had the best brother in the world. You wouldn't even deserve to be in his shadow.
Juan-Yun: ...Is that so? Then I hope he never finds out how you died. From the way you talk about him... I'd hate to have to kill him too.
Juan-Yun: As for you, the adorable little princess of the Rune Academy...
Juan-Yun: Enough. This is your destiny. If I were you, I'd have gone right back to the Kingdom of the Sun to catch the last of the peaceful days.
Juan-Yun: You can't win. Don't even bother trying. This time, victory is sure to be ours.
Tica: (Miss Sione... I'm sorry... I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry...)
Tica: (...Tica Chevalier, you must not cry. Your friends are still relying on you.)
Tica: I've got to find Pang and the Tiger Tribe and tell them the truth about what happened... Now's not the time for more clashes with the Insects.
